or values of x from - infinity to -0.1985050494  and from 4.317817450 \+
to - infinity.\nd.y intercept is 6.\ne.As x approaches - infinity, f11
 approaches - infinity. As x approaches + infinity, f11 approaches - i
nfinity.\nf. Critical point is where x=-1 and x=3.\ng.The local maximu
m is (3,249).\nh.There is no local minimum, but there is a point of 0 \+
slope at (-1,-7).\ni. The function values are increasing for values of
 x from (-1,4.317817450).\nj. The function values are decreasing for v
alues of x from (- infinity,-1) and from (4.317817450,+ infinity)." }}
